{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f4f2d2869","title":"致全体战地司令员命令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"247c4dcae1","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":1,"articleId":"4f4f2d2869"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"362f049989","type":"paragraph","text":"致全体战地司令员命令！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"4f4f2d2869"},{"id":"9812859f9f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月1日）共产党员、全体战地司令员：在任何地点，如果国民党军队不攻击我军，我军即不应主动地政击国民党军，但如被攻击，我军将坚持采取自卫手段，以保护人民之生命财产，并维持民主政府的法令。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"4f4f2d2869"},{"id":"88a5fb310c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"4f4f2d2869"},{"id":"2c402fe17a","type":"paragraph","text":"七月一日[11蒋介石7月1日通过广播演说公开发布给各地战区长官的命令，声称：“如共军不进攻我军，则我军亦不进攻共军。”这是毛泽东针对裤介石发","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"4f4f2d2869"}],"page":{"id":"a34e21ff33","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"4f4f2d2869","start":452,"end":452}}}},"__N_SSG":true}